$date
  2026-06-20T00:00:00Z
$end
$version
  WaveCrux Stage - Tachometer custom-widget demo
$end
$comment
  Drives the Tachometer / Community Gauge custom widget: an 8-bit
  rpm ramp, a redline that asserts in the upper range, and shift
  pulses simulating gear changes. Bind rpm->rpm, redline->redline,
  shift->shift.
$end
$timescale 1 ns $end
$scope module gauge_demo $end
$var wire 8 ! rpm $end
$var wire 1 " redline $end
$var wire 1 # shift $end
$upscope $end
$enddefinitions $end
